ARE 1.0.0!
- Initial release of the ARE (Another Rust Editor).
- Features include:
  - Syntax highlighting for multiple programming languages.
  - Code completion and suggestions.
  - Integrated terminal for running commands.
  - Customizable themes and layouts.
  - Support for plugins and extensions.
- Known issues:
  - Some features may be unstable or not fully implemented.
- Future plans:
  - Implementing a built-in debugger.
  - Adding support for more programming languages.
- Contributions are welcome! Please submit pull requests or report issues on the GitHub repository.